ex|last=Ballinger|publisher=CyclingWeekly|date=13 March 2020|accessdate=13 March 2020}}</ref>}}\n{{cyclingresult|1|[[Tiesj Benoot]]|BEL|{{ct|SUN|2020}}|3h 57' 02\"}}\n{{cyclingresult|2|[[Michael Matthews (cyclist)|Michael Matthews]]|AUS|{{ct|SUN|2020}}|+ 22\"}}\n{{cyclingresult|3|[[Sergio Higuita]]|COL|{{ct|EFD|2020}}|+ 22\"|[[File:Jersey white.svg|20px]]}}\n{{cyclingresult|4|[[Bob Jungels]]|LUX|{{ct|QST|2020}}|+ 22\"}}\n{{cyclingresult|5|[[Julian Alaphilippe]]|FRA|{{ct|QST|2020}}|+ 22\"}}\n{{cyclingresult|6|[[Vincenzo Nibali]]|ITA|{{ct|TFS|2020}}|+ 22\"}}\n{{cyclingresult|7|[[Thibaut Pinot]]|FRA|{{ct|GFC|2020}}|+ 22\"}}\n{{cyclingresult|8|[[Guillaume Martin]]|FRA|{{ct|COF|2020}}|+ 22\"}}\n{{cyclingresult|9|[[Rudy Molard]]|FRA|{{ct|GFC|2020}}|+ 22\"}}\n{{cyclingresult|10|[[Nairo Quintana]]|COL|{{ct|FST|2020}}|+ 22\"}}\n{{cyclingresult end}}\n||\n{{cyclingresult start|title=General classification after Stage 6<ref name=\"Result-S6\" /><ref name=\"CW-S6\" />}}\n{{cyclingresult|1|[[Maximilian Schachmann]]|GER|{{ct|BOH|2020}}|22h 46' 24\"|[[File:Jersey yellow.svg|20px]][[File:Jersey green.svg|20px]]}}\n{{cyclingresult|2|[[Tiesj Benoot]]|BEL|{{ct|SUN|2020}}|+ 36\"|[[File:Jersey yellow number.svg|20px]]}}\n{{cyclingresult|3|[[Sergio Higuita]]|COL|{{ct|EFD|2020}}|+ 1' 01\"|[[File:Jersey white.svg|20px]]}}\n{{cyclingresult|4|[[Felix Gro\u00dfschartner]]|AUT|{{ct|BOH|2020}}|+ 1' 01\"}}\n{{cyclingresult|5|[[Michael Matthews (cyclist)|Michael Matthews]]|AUS|{{ct|SUN|2020}}|+ 1' 10\"|[[File:Jersey yellow number.svg|20px]]}}\n{{cyclingresult|6|[[Vincenzo Nibali]]|ITA|{{ct|TFS|2020}}|+ 1' 18\"}}\n{{cyclingresult|7|[[Rudy Molard]]|FRA|{{ct|GFC|2020}}|+ 1' 29\"}}\n{{cyclingresult|8|[[Thibaut Pinot]]|FRA|{{ct|GFC|2020}}|+ 1' 30\"}}\n{{cyclingresult|9|[[Tanel Kangert]]|EST|{{ct|EFD|2020}}|+ 1' 52\"}}\n{{cyclingresult|10|[[Julian Alaphilippe]]|FRA|{{ct|QST|2020}}|+ 2' 04\"}}\n{{cyclingresult end}}\n|}\n\n===Stage 7===\n;14 March 2020&nbsp;\u2014 [[Nice]] to [[Valdeblore|Valdeblore La 